<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4761657>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 33. Gonopod. A) Eucampesmella lartiguei lartiguei (Silvestri, 1897) (MNRJ 11609); B) Angelodesmus costalimai Schubart, 1962(holotype, MZSP); C)Arthrosolaenomeris sacin. sp. (IBSP 1148); D) Abiliodesmusmapinguari n. sp.(CZUFMT 836); E) Gangugia simplex Schubart, 1958 (holotype, MZSP 1077); F) A. saci n. sp. (IBSP 1148). Scale bars: B–E) 1 mm.; A, F) 0,5 mm. Black bars refer to the degree of angulation of the prefemoral process. Abbreviations: Cx, gonocoxae; dl, dorso-basal lobe of the prefemoral process; Pf, prefemoral region; PfP, prefemoral process; S, solenomere." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4761657/files/figure.png" .

